Data ingestion

Student grades

grades <- read_xlsx("student-grades.xlsx") %>%
  rename_with(
    ~ tolower(
      gsub(" ", "_",
        stri_trans_general(str = .x, id = "Latin-ASCII"),
        fixed = TRUE
      )
    )
  ) %>%
  select(
    ten_hoc_sinh, `truong...5`, `hk1/22`, `xep_loai...7`, `hk2/23`,
    `xep_loai...9`, ca_nam_2023, `xep_loai...11`
  ) %>%
  rename(
    name = ten_hoc_sinh,
    school = `truong...5`,
    sem1 = `hk1/22`,
    sem1_desc = `xep_loai...7`,
    sem2 = `hk2/23`,
    sem2_desc = `xep_loai...9`,
    yearly = ca_nam_2023,
    yearly_desc = `xep_loai...11`
  )

Student extra information

info <- read_xlsx("student-info.xlsx", skip = 1) %>%
  rename_with(
    ~ tolower(
      gsub(" ", "_",
        stri_trans_general(str = .x, id = "Latin-ASCII"),
        fixed = TRUE
      )
    )
  ) %>%
  select(ho_va_ten, truong_dang_hoc, hoan_canh_gia_dinh) %>%
  rename(
    name = ho_va_ten,
    school = truong_dang_hoc,
    cond = hoan_canh_gia_dinh
  ) %>%
  mutate(cond_code = case_match(cond, "Kh khn" ~ 0, "Rt kh khn" ~ 10))

EDA

Students grade between grading periods

grades %>%
  pivot_longer(
    -c(name, school, sem1_desc, sem2_desc, yearly_desc),
    names_to = "period", values_to = "grade"
  ) %>% mutate(
    period = case_match(period, "sem1" ~ "Semester 1", "sem2" ~ "Semester 2", "yearly" ~ "Year")
  ) -> grades_long

grades_long %>%
  group_by(grade, period) %>%
  tally() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = grade, y = n, fill = period)) +
  geom_col() +
  facet_wrap(~period, ncol = 1) + 
  ggtitle("Student's grade between grading periods") + 
  scale_fill_discrete("Grading period") + 
  scale_x_continuous("Grade") + 
  scale_y_continuous("Student count")

Students grade change between semesters

sem_diff_df <- grades %>%
  mutate(sem_diff = sem2 - sem1) %>%
  arrange(sem_diff) %>%
  drop_na() %>%
  mutate(order = seq(1, length(name)))

sem_diff_df %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_segment(
    aes(x = order, xend = order, y = 0, yend = sem_diff, color = sem_diff),
    linewidth = 2
  ) +
  scale_y_continuous("Grade change", breaks = seq(-1, 2, 0.5)) +
  scale_x_discrete("", breaks = NULL) + 
  theme(legend.position = "none") + 
  ggtitle("Student's grade change between semesters")

sem_diff_df %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_segment(
    aes(x = order, xend = order, y = 0, yend = sem_diff, color = school),
    linewidth = 2
  ) +
  scale_y_continuous("Grade change", breaks = seq(-1, 2, 0.5)) +
  scale_x_discrete("", breaks = NULL) + 
  scale_color_discrete("School") + 
  ggtitle("Student's grade change between semesters")

Students distribution by school

school_df <- grades %>%
  group_by(school) %>%
  tally() %>%
  mutate(coord = case_match(
    school,
    "Bnh n" ~ "10.362403126853797, 106.73955437027948",
    "L Quc Vit" ~ "10.38159261387887, 106.70346739495444",
    "Nguyn Trng Dn" ~ "10.34439085884802, 106.70390091842829",
    "Phng Thanh Vn" ~ "10.434243045923658, 106.71420856927784",
    "THPT Chuyn Tin Giang" ~ "10.365939280759616, 106.33950912448732",
    "THPT G Cng ng" ~ "10.397468900847956, 106.71589633369517",
    "THPT Nguyn Vn Cn" ~ "10.316834652373718, 106.71644825096531",
    "TTGDTX G Cng ng" ~ "10.326821445306106, 106.71819370031828",
    "Thi Vn Nam" ~ "10.400463682054077, 106.74909998415183",
    "V Duy Linh" ~ "10.292109230044234, 106.77615583255589",
    "V Vn Chnh" ~ "10.40235281920347, 106.7155538645969",
    "V Vn Dnh" ~ "10.30982939092137, 106.71406118931955",
    "V Vn Kit" ~ "10.354969902443996, 106.75602352141257",
    "on Hng Phc" ~ "10.412368840294398, 106.76771534550913"
  )) %>%
  separate_wider_delim(
    coord, ",",
    names = c("Y", "X")
  ) %>%
  mutate(X = as.double(X), Y = as.double(Y)) %>%
  left_join(
    grades %>%
      drop_na(yearly) %>%
      group_by(school) %>%
      summarise(avg_yearly = mean(yearly)),
    by = "school"
  )
